org.eclipse.nvplayout.model

Class CalibrationVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.nvplayout.model.CalibrationVariable

  • public class CalibrationVariable
extends java.lang.Object
    CalibrationVariable is the last layer of the model.
    This model contain the definition of a variable block, i-e :
    • Alias in RAM.
    • The address of the variable.
    • The value of the variable in decimal.
    • The Type of variable (uint8, sint8, uint16, ...).
    • The size of the variable, link to the type. automatically set.
    • The unit of the variable.
    • The description of the variable.
    • The low limit of the value range.
    • The high limit of the value range.
    • The requirement of the variable.

    Based on a MVC model

    Version:
    0.0 Alpha EarlyAccess Beta Tester
    Author:
    GLI feat Software Team
